{"tid":940690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄教科書刪侵中國領土歷史　華不出聲","createTime":"2018-12-14T06:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T07:12:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf063dd4d45d27fee03b5f30ce0d16bc8f0363c","tid":940690,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181214/20568423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F20568423&d=NgsX4dvaM60oeQzAHgI6lC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=dce28b0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F20568423&h=a617594e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181214/20568423</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月14日 <br />\n<br />\n俄教科書刪侵中國領土歷史　華不出聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181214/large/14cx08p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181214%2Flarge%2F14cx08p.jpg&h=c1682d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俄羅斯教科書刪去侵佔中國領土的史實，但中國無反應。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n親疏有別，立場有異！俄羅斯國民中學歷史教科書出版商為避免爭議，最近將18、19世紀侵佔中國領土的內容修除，獲得俄國當局與學術界一致認同。與俄稱兄道弟的中國至今默不作聲。但北京卻多次譴責日本修改教科書，隱瞞侵華歷史真相。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n刪去「俄佔遠東阿穆爾」字句<br />\n<br />\n根據俄官媒報道，該國遠東地區城市、與中國黑河市隔黑龍江相望的海蘭泡（Hailan Boo），有家長對其子女在學校學習的歷史教科書中，關於俄國掠奪了中國領土的措辭感到憤怒，提出抗議並要求修改。有關課本的內容提到「歐洲人急於利用中國的混亂狀態，1857年到1860年，英法對中國發動了第二次鴉片戰爭，並獲得中國內部通商權，俄國佔領遠東阿穆爾地區，法國得到一部份附庸中國的越南，日本得到一些島嶼。英法部隊成功地鎮壓太平天國的起義」。負責編纂國中歷史科教科書的出版社「啟蒙運動」得知消息後，把「俄國佔領遠東阿穆爾地區」整句刪去；阿穆爾州教育和科學部則說，教科書是國家核定的教材，修改內容並無違法，未來將繼續給俄羅斯國中八年級學生使用。<br />\n<br />\n中國東北大片領土被俄羅斯侵佔的歷史，一直是中國人心中永遠的痛。但俄方一直試圖對此淡化和隱瞞。早前，有中國退伍軍人、獨立研究人員殷敏鴻向中外交部兩度提告，指控政府刻意隱瞞領土被俄國侵佔，不料被北京高等法院打回票稱「人民無權知道國土版圖」，引發網友譏笑「中國一點也不能少，但是可以缺一大塊」。<br />\n<br />\n塔斯社/《自由時報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n南京大屠殺81周年　落實公祭法必須默哀"},{"pid":"cce45d9d270543e1264f730411300f746ecc6c3d","tid":940690,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"人地打滿清關你共產黨撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d969097901c2cfb3a21a4bcc4f2a36860b9bf02a","tid":940690,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:49:54.000Z","msg":"永遠做蛾蝗隻契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039966f0c424d95ab51a019507eb8b8b7f37f937","tid":940690,"uid":57554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:53:07.000Z","msg":"蛾克蝗，定律黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0a383bccff2ffcf6ac78cdb8bdf7058d97e882","tid":940690,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"事實黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26feff1c17fc5f5d2bf3b2e57e6dee2085d839c","tid":940690,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:58:03.000Z","msg":"咩侵略啊 送出去架喎 你叫口交部點解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0366c4f0411b61516054f052385511913dc6b1c","tid":940690,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"蛾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1c0bfcd816eecaf6bc85412d123049bc0d6cde","tid":940690,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"國人無權得知領土範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97fc3dcb18bb8d9325238e0694cdd8c036be2f4","tid":940690,"uid":17753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外交部呢喂 平時好快㗎"},{"pid":"8555512fc5195db63afb5f13ae8b2c0c81494490","tid":940690,"uid":222140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"中國人只敢對同自己差不多樣的種族玩"},{"pid":"5e1aa0f23dcba9df7fb0ef01fd5af7bb931ce454","tid":940690,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"中國奶帝俄屎忽真係憝唔明 歷來俄國出名廢同無口齒"}]}